short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Displays debug information for Alma's View It menu

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Use this plugin to troubleshoot the UResolver menu. A bug icon will appear in the upper-right corner of the "view it" menu. Clicking on the bug will load menu in "debug mode", which enables you to see the context object metadata, a complete list of target services, and whether or not the services have been filtered for any reason.
